==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Plucker
<hw>Pluck"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that
which, plucks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou setter up and <qex>plucker</qex> down of kings.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A machine for straightening and cleaning
wool.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plucker tube</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Pluecker tube</ent>⟦br⟧
